---
title: Palak Chicken Breast Curry with Basmati Rice and Crispy Onions
description: 'Palak' is Hindi for spinach, the iron-rich leafy green in this mildly spiced, creamy curry - not to be confused with 'saag', which means any kind of leafy greens! Chicken is the perfect vehicle for soaking up the delicious flavours.
